===Etymology 2===
{{G.}} [[quarc]]

====Noun====
'''quark'''

# a soft [[cream]]y [[cheese]]. The Russian quark and Finnish quark are somewhat different. The Russian version is firmer in consistency and contains about 15% milk fat, whereas the Finnish quark often contains less than 1% milk fat. 

